  "keyFeatures": [
    "JWT authentication with access tokens and HttpOnly refresh token cookies",
    "Backtracking algorithm that generates top 3 optimized schedule combinations",
    "Priority-based rule scoring system with 11 configurable rule types",
    "Two-phase optimization: pruning (hard constraints) followed by backtracking with scoring",
    "Full CRUD for subjects, professors, sections, and scheduling rules",
    "Save and manage generated schedules",
    "Swagger/OpenAPI documentation at /docs",
    "PostgreSQL database with Prisma ORM"
  ],
